Who amongst us can’t resist the charm of authentic French Provençal kitchen design assembled from genuine antique building materials? We hope to highlight in this blog few quintessential French Provençal kitchens with all their distinctive architectural elements and appointments.

It’s been said, that heartfelt homemade cuisine is made with authentic ingredients, patience and love.
